Oh I agree.  This change is great for people who don't group with enchanters, mostly because it makes us unnecessary.  However, ask them how they would feel if SOE did something to them that made their class unnecessary, and I think you would see a similar reaction to what you see here.
<br />

<br />
I can't really understand defending this poorly executed nerf on the grounds of "class balance."  Do I think they were trying to balance things?  Sure, and I even agree with what they were trying to do to a certain extent.  Do I think what they did was the right thing to do?  Hell no.
<br />

<br />
The road to Hell is paved with good intentions.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=824212" target="_blank" class="postlink">Visionary Provender</a>, High Elf Coercer (retired)
