                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Yeah, I guess if you don't see things from an enchanter's point of view, then you probably won't think enchanters are bad off.    Millionaires sitting around sipping brandy might ask 'is being homeless really that bad, I mean hey look at me I'm fat and happy how could someone else not be?'   
