    Lets face it, SoE didn't burst into your living room and saw your legs off with a rusty hacksaw -- so things could be worse.   However, this is a game that many have a lot of time and money invested so there is some room to get a tad unhappy about things that directly affect the few remaining reasons they invest said time/money.
<br />

<br />
    If SoE was producing a tangible product, say cars for instance, their asses would've been slapped with 1000 class action law suits by now for all the bumbling over the years, to put it into a consumer's perspective.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
